&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We are Mythical Games. A Venture-backed next-generation game technology company at the intersection of video games and economics led by industry veterans. Our goal is to lead the industry with the launch of exceptional video game experiences that leverage distributed ledger technology, while also providing a platform of robust tools that will allow any other game developers to do the same.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We are actively seeking a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Senior Program Manager, People &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;to join our growing People team.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
